<span class="line"><span>			[wwwroot]path = /var/www/htmlcomment = www.xykj.comread only = yesdont compress   = *.gz *.tgz *.zip *.z *.Z *.rpm *.deb *.bz2auth users = backupersecrets file = /etc/rsyncd_users.db</span></span>
